Detailed Description

cvmx_pcsx::_control1_reg

NOTE: Logic Analyzer is enabled with LA_EN for the specified PCS lane only. PKT_SZ is effective only when LA_EN=1 For normal operation(sgmii or 1000Base-X), this bit must be 0. See pcsx.csr for xaui logic analyzer mode. For full description see document at .../rtl/pcs/readme_logic_analyzer.txt

PCSX regs follow IEEE Std 802.3-2005, Section: 45.2.3

PCSX_CONTROL1_REG = Control Register1
